Amino acids properties

Source: R/doc_data.R
AAindex.Rd

Raw and normalized (0-1) 554 amino acid properties as retrieved from AAIndex database (release 9.1).

Format

A data frames with 20 columns and 600 rows.

Source

AAIndex database.
